Class Attachment

java.lang.Object
  dk.aau.cs.giraf.TimerLib.Attachment
Direct Known Subclasses:
SingleImg, SplitImg, Timer
public class Attachment
extends java.lang.Object

Attachment is a super class, and is used for attaching an extra timer, a pictogram next to a timer, or replacing the default pictogram on done screen Layer: Tools
